data.text:
This high dynamic range (HDR) photograph brings out the natural beauty in the picture perfect mountainous landscape of Iceland. Wonderful colours and reflections in the lake create an exceptional art print with plenty of detail. This picture is available as a classic canvas print, an elegant framed art print, or a sophisticated floating-style glossy acrylic.

Photography by Dirk Paessler.

Only logged in customers who have purchased this product may leave a review.

At Fotoviva Art Prints we deliver your art prints for FREE to UK mainland addresses. That applies to our canvas prints, acrylics and framed art. If you wish to order from further afield please contact us for a shipping estimate.
